trans-unit.source: Specifies how the content in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal"></xref> control is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvordan innhold i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal"> </xref> kontrollen gjengis.

trans-unit.source: The LiteralMode enumeration represents the modes that you can specify for how the content in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control is rendered.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen LiteralMode representerer modusene kan du angi hvordan innholdet i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen gjengis.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Mode%2A> property uses these enumeration values to set the behavior of the contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Mode%2A>disse nummereringsverdier bruker til å angi virkemåte for innholdet i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>egenskap i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Mode%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `PassThrough`, the entire contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property are passed to the device or browser without any modifications.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir `PassThrough`, hele innholdet i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>egenskapen er sendt til enheten eller nettleseren uten noen endringer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control contains an `<hr>` tag, it is sent to all devices and browsers regardless of whether it is supported.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen inneholder en `<hr>` koden, sendes på alle enheter og nettlesere uavhengig om det støttes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `Encode`, the contents for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property are converted into an HTML-encoded string before rendering.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir `Encode`, innholdet for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>egenskapen blir konvertert til en HTML-kodet streng før gjengivelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control contains an `<hr>` tag, it will be converted to `<hr>` and sent to the device or browser.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen inneholder en `<hr>` kode, vil bli konvertert til `<hr>` og sendes til enheten eller nettleser.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you specify `Transform`, the rendering behavior of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property depends on the type of markup being rendered.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir `Transform`, gjengivelse virkemåten for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>egenskapen er avhengig av hva slags markup gjengitt.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control is rendered for a device or browser that supports HTML or XHTML, specifying Transform produces the same behavior as specifying PassThrough.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen gjengis for en enhet eller nettleser som støtter HTML eller XHTML, angi transformering produserer på samme måte som angir PassThrough.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>

trans-unit.source: All markup tags and elements for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property are rendered for the requesting browser.
trans-unit.target: Alle koder og -elementer for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>egenskapen gjengis for anmoder leseren.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control is rendered for a markup language other than HTML or XHTML, such as WML or cHTML, you can use the Transform value to remove unsupported markup elements.
trans-unit.target: Når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen gjengis for en markup language enn HTML eller XHTML, for eksempel WML eller cHTML, kan du bruke verdien transformering fjerne Ustøttet markeringselementer.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>

trans-unit.source: In this case, any markup-language elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property that are not supported in the targeted markup language are not rendered for the control.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet noen markup language-elementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>-egenskap som ikke støttes i den angitte markup language ikke gjengis for kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control contains an `<hr>` tag, the tag is removed before the content is sent to a WML device.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>for en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>kontrollen inneholder en `<hr>` koden, koden fjernes før innholdet sendes til en enhet som WML.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>

trans-unit.source: If an unsupported tag contains content, only the tag is removed and the content is sent to the device or browser.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en Ustøttet koden inneholder innhold, fjernes bare koden og innholdet som er sendt til enheten eller nettleser.

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property contains the content `<XYZ>Test</XYZ>`, the `<XYZ>` and `</XYZ>` tags are removed while the text `Test` is sent to the device or browser.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel hvis den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>egenskapen inneholder innholdet `<XYZ>Test</XYZ>`, `<XYZ>` og `</XYZ>` koder er fjernet under teksten `Test` sendes til enheten eller nettleser.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>

trans-unit.target: Litteralen kontrollens innhold som HTML-kodet.
